Be serious...

You like Misty right?

I mean OBVIOUSLY (well hopefully) not as much as you love me.

But you guys are all kissy kissy nice again, right?

Don't lie to me.

"Is that a girl...or a guy?"
She stared intently as we glared at the stage and the screen, "I dunno, but if its a guy he's cute." =D
Silly people...

and then you watched my eye change shapes...maybe we were sitting a little to close to the people on drugs because as I look back you werevery amused.

I just figured I'd say...

*waves*

Hi...

I am making you a CD and I am gonna mail it to you and it's gonna rock...well maybe not...but you'll pretend because you LOVE ME...ad if you dont you'll fake that too

OMG I can't believe we had to watch that stupid movie on how to turn on and off a computer and use a mouse. Just getting the damn VCR to work was what we need to learn. "The left button is the one that will be primarely used...blah blah blah." That summer was the first I'd heard the phrase "kick it"...remember that guy who was in a gang and kept saying we should go kick it and he'd give us the codes to sim city. So fun...we got A's because we sucked up and lmao remember the morphing thing we had to do and we turned a man into a dog or something and we spent like 4 days on that and it was a peice of crap but she loved it...omg yay.

I love you Carissa!!! We can have fun with this...or if not....uhhh...we can write things that remind of us of each other and things we've done together...and funny stories...good times...no no no ...excellent times!!!

muah.
